Tis the season to give... So, I teamed up with @fairparkdallas to giveaway a pair of tickets to @EnchantDallas 
 🌟 🎁 🎄 
@enchantdallas is a winter wonderland featuring the worlds largest Christmas light maze, an ice skating ring and a Christmas market! Santa 🎅🏻 is also there for the kiddos.  To enter:
• Like this post
• Follow @fairparkdallas 
• Comment with who you’d bring (each comment is one ent
ry)

I will contact the winner on December 23.

As always thanks for supporting me and my work!!
Happy Holidays from Big D! 🎁#dallas #dallastx #dfw #dallasphotographer #happyholidays #christmas #dallastexas #happyholiday
